Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}（序幕）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{渐显部分好像是变速的}{\fad(1300,1000)\1c&H00111111}（极北之地 1857年）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,船长！\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,船长！\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,能谈谈吗？\NCan we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{【感觉可以省略这句】}嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不破冰船没法动了\NWe must break through the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都又累又饿\NThe men are hungry and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,继续这样下去 恐怕损失很大\NWe cannot keep up this pace without consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙听着！\NListen up, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拖得越久 冰就冻得越牢\NThe more we delay the labor, the firmer the grasp of the ice will become.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧干\NThe work continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,分组轮流休息\NRotate each group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 请听我说\NSir, with respect…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙想听一句准话\NThe men need assurances.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,准话？\NAssurances?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对 就是船能动之后 我们掉头回圣彼得堡\NYes, that we will head back to St. Petersburg once we free the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们觉得我们的船航行不了多久了 他们想知道…\NThey don't think we'll be seaworthy for long and they want to know--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,都听好了！\NListen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别的事情 都不需要你们和这位长官该操心\NIt is neither your place, nor the officer here, to think anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,任务确定了 你们也接受了 那就把它做完\NWe signed up for a mission and we will see it to completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定能到达北极的\NWe will reach the North Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,都听明白了吗？\NIs it understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,船长 那边有爆炸…\NAn explosion, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大约三公里\NAbout two miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,去救人\NGet the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,雪橇犬没受伤\NThe sled dogs are unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那这血是谁的？\NThen where does all this blood come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,船长 在那里！\NOver here, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有个人受伤了 流了好多血\NA wounded man, he's lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,肩膀有伤 腿也断了\NWound to the shoulder, his leg is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被熊咬的？\NBear attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不是 船长\NI don't think so, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,拉森 把这只靴子弄下来\NLarsen, help me with his boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是个假肢\NA prosthetic leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把他抬回船上去\NPut him on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快 抬上船 赶紧！\NHurry! To the ship! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拉森 那东西来了\NLarsen, that thing is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,步枪准备！\NReady the rifles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,听我指令\NOn my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准！\NAim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,开火！\NFire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,下一组！\NNext group!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,开火！\NFire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,全部上船！\NAll to the ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,抬回来那个人呢？\NWhere is that man we brought onboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪？\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那究竟是什么东西？它想怎么？\NWhat is that thing? What does it want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,把他交给我！\NBring him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喇叭枪 拉森 拿喇叭枪！\NThe blunderbuss. Larsen, get the blunderbuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了它\NI killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了它\NI killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它还活着！\NIt's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,梯子！\NLadder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快收梯子！\NPull up the ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把他交出来！\NBring him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩几发？\NHow many shots are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一发 这杀不死它啊\NOne, but it can't kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要打他\NI'm not aiming for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是鸦片酊 能止痛 喝吧\NLaudanum, to ease the pain. Drink it. Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是在哪里？\NWhere am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在丹麦皇家霍莱松特号船上\NYou are on the Royal Danish ship, Horisont.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是安德森船长 这位是邬德森医生\NI'm Captain Anderson. This is Dr. Udsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那怪物杀了你们多少人？\NHow many of your men did it kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,六个\NSix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它还会回来的 还会有人丧命\NIt will come back and kill many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把我交出去吧 不然你们都会没命的\NAll of you, if necessary, unless you deliver me to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的 它回不来了\NNo, no. It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它沉进冰水里 肯定冻死了\NIt sank in the freezing waters. It's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它还没死！\NNo, it is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它死不了的\NIt cannot die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直试着彻底干掉它\NI have tried to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你们信不信\NWhether you believe me or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它都会回来 找我\Nit will come back… for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等它真的回来了\NAnd when it does,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须把我放到外面的冰上\Nyou must promise that you will put me out on the ice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,让它把我带走\Nand let it take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,求你们了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什么东西？\NWhat manner of creature is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪个魔鬼创造出来的？\NWhat manner of devil made him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是我创造的\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是我亲手创造的他\NI made him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我本已下定决心 让那些罪恶的记忆和我一同消亡\NI had determined that the memory of my evils should die with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了\NIt's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我要说的话 有些听起来像真的\NSome of what I will tell you is fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有些听起来像假的 但都是事实\NSome is not, but it is all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫维克多\NMy name is Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多·弗兰肯斯坦\NVictor Frankenstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲给我起的名字\NIt was my father who gave me that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这名字的寓意吗？\NDo you know what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是征服者的意思\NI believe I do, yes. Conqueror.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,赢得一切的人\NOne that wins it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 一切都因他而起\NYes. It all started with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲\NMy father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我母亲\NAnd my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（第一部分 维克多的故事）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快下来 你父亲来了\NCome down, your father is arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈? \NMaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲 我在这里\NI'm here, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\NI'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲是男爵 也是个杰出的外科医生\NMy father was a baron and a preeminent surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他娶我母亲 很大程度上为了利益\NHe had married my mother largely out of convenience,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为母亲的陪嫁相当丰厚 而且她是贵族出身\Nas her dowry was considerable and her lineage noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她带来的资金 足以让父亲维持爵位和家族产业\NIt furnished my father with the means to preserve his rank and family estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,日常生活中 从来看不见父亲的身影\NHe was absent from our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而每当他回到家 所有人都对他唯命是从\Nbut when he came home, the entire household bent to his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的克莱尔\NClaire, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在的时候…\NThe rest of the time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\NFather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在的时候 母亲就是我一个人的\NThe rest of the time, Mother was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别拿走 端到这里来\NNo, bring that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,肉里的盐分能滋养你的血液\NThe salts in the meat will enrich your blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还有胎儿的\Nas well as the baby's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一人吃 两人补 记得吗？\NYou eat for two, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧\NGo on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很有营养\NIt's nutritious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,守护天使\NGuardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,甜蜜的陪伴\NSweet companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请守护我 不要离开我\NStand by my side and do not leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的披风庇护我 然后…\NUnder your mantle, shelter me, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我隔着墙听到他们争论不休\NI would hear them through the wall, arguing incessantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对着彼此大吼大叫 话题关于财富和庄园 还有我\Nyelling at each other about wealth, estate… and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的争吵声让我万分恐惧\NTheir voices filled me with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈?\NMaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈?\NMaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人鄙视我们两个\NThe man despised us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌我们乌黑的头发、深色的瞳孔\NOur raven black hair, our deep, dark eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就连我们喜好安静、不时紧张的性情\NEven our quiet, at times nervous disposition
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎也会让他大为光火\Nseemed to exasperate him to no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,古代把体液分为哪几类？\NList as accurately as you can the ancient classification
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量说精确一点\Nof the humors in the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,血液、黑胆汁、黄胆汁和黏液\NBlood, black bile, yellow bile, and phlegm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,男性心脏的平均重量是多少？\NAverage male heart. Weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,250到310克 父亲\NNine to eleven ounces, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,女性心脏的平均重量？\NAverage female heart. Weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,230到280克\NEight to ten ounces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得\NWhy do you suppose that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,女性的心脏会轻一点？\NDifference in mass in female heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为她们情感更强烈？\NDepth of emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,更容易忧郁吗？\NTendency to the melancholic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为质量 血流量 肌肉灌注的不同 父亲\NMass. Volume of blood, Father. Muscular irrigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 人体组织中没有精神物质\NQuite. There is no spiritual content in tissue,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,肌肉中没有情感\Nand no emotion in a muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 请描述一下三尖瓣的主要功能\NNow, describe the main function of the tricuspid valve, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在想不起来了 父亲 但我肯定能想起来\NI cannot recall, Father, but I'm sure I will remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我相信你\NYeah, I'm sure you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,象牙不会流血 维克多\NIvory does not bleed, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但人体会\NFlesh does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等你想起了某个知识要点 恐怕你的病人已经一命呜呼了\NBy the time you remember a fact, your patient could be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗？\NYou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,三尖瓣的主要功能\NThe main function of the tricuspid valve
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是防止血液反流至腔静脉\Nis to prevent the reflux of blood into the vena cava.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不打手了 再也不打了\NNo, not your hands. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它们如今是你施展技艺的工具 是你意志的延伸\NThey are now the instruments of your craft and will,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好保护\Nand we must care for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而你的脸 就微不足道了\NYour face, however, is vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多 你沿用了我的名字 也必然要维护我的名声\NYou bear my name, Victor, and with it my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我恳请你牢记这一点\NI pray you remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉你有很好的牌\NI feel you have something very good, parce que…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,三\NThree…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,二\NTwo…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一\NOne…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\NThat's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我来洗牌\NI'll shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲？\NMother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈?\NMaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\NFather!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 母亲不好了\NFather. It's Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,多准备一些热水和干净的亚麻布 快\NI need hot water and clean linen. A lot of it. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 维克多 -妈妈？\N-No, Victor! -Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-妈妈! -维克多!\N-Maman! -Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲！父亲！\NFather! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,救救她 求你了！\NSave her, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲 她是我生命一部分\NMy mother, whom I had come to consider a part of my very self,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾以为她永远不会离去\Nshe who I thought would never leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,以为她是我的生命 如今她死了\Nshe who was life… was now death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她的双眼已暗淡无光\NHer eyes extinguished,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,笑容被冰冷的土地埋葬\Nher smile feeding the cold earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,走开！\NLeave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我走开！\NAll of you, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的世界空了一块\NA part of the universe had been hollowed out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的头顶笼罩着永远的黑暗\Nand the firmament was now permanently dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,遮住眼睛\NNow, cover your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你看再看哦\NDon't look until I tell you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧\NNow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉在阳光和笑容中长大\NWilliam grew full of sunshine and smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他的性情比我平和温顺 显然更讨父亲喜欢\NHe was of a calmer, gentler disposition, clearly favored by my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 父亲\NThank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气 儿子\NOh, it's a pleasure, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他是宜人的微风 我是滚滚的黑云\NHe was the breeze, I was the storm cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他带来欢声笑语 我让人愁眉不展\NHe was all laughter, I was all frowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拿起缰绳\NPick up the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 看我做得怎么样\NLook at me, Father. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不止如此\NThere was something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,更确切地说 某些东西被忽视了\NOr rather, something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我的母亲\NMy mother had died
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,死在如日中天的名医\Nat the hands of the most distinguished doctor of his day:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父亲手下\NMy father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脑中渐渐有了个想法\NAn idea… took shape in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,请说说《心血运动论》中…\NDefine the circulatory system, if you will…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,无可避免 无法逃避\NInevitable, unavoidable…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,…对循环系统是怎么定义的\N…as enunciated in De Motu Cordis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,…直到这个想法被说了出来\N…until it became truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲？\NFather?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你没救她 对吗？\NYou let her die, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我用尽全力救她了 你必须知道这一点\NI did everything in my power to save her. You must know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说 你失败了\NSo you failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能战胜死亡\N-No one can conquer death. -Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我能 我会战胜的\NI will. I will conquer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我会掌握你掌握的所有知识 还会更进一步\NEverything you know, I will know. And more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就到此为止吧\NI think we've done quite enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那晚我重生了\NI was born anew that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了幻象\NI had a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次看到了\NI saw, for the first time…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗天使\Nthe Dark Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它向我许下承诺\NAnd it made me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我将能掌控生死\NI would have command over the forces of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,成为和父亲一样杰出的外科医生\NI would become every ounce the surgeon my father was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的野心和成就将超过他\NI would surpass him in ambition and in reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,守护天使\NGuardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,幻象如此清晰\NThe vision was so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,无论清醒还是睡梦中 我都从未看到如此清晰的景象\NClearer than anything I'd ever seen in my waking hours or dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但承诺如何兑现？\NBut how?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的境遇很快一落千丈\NMy downfall was swift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲的种植园 经历了两次叛乱和一场火灾\NTwo revolts and a fire on my mother's plantations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,家族财富因此锐减\Ndwindled the family fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,庄园留下了 但别的全都没了\NWe kept the estate, but lost everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉被送去了维也纳的亲戚家\NWilliam went to one side of the family in Vienna
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了伦敦 然后又去了爱丁堡\Nand I to London, then Edinburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里 我花了数十年时间\NAnd there, for decades, I tried to…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,尝试为狭隘的学术界拓宽边界\Nexpand the narrow limits of academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,生命\NLife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是生命 先生们\NThis… is life, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,（皇家医学院纪律法庭 1855年）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出生了\NWe are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,刚上去没多久 就掉下来了\NAnd no sooner do we rise, we fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,死了\NDeath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这一起一落之间\NAnd in the space between that rise and fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我们渺小卑微的一生\Nour humble little purview.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,出生不为我们所控\NNow, birth is not in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对？\NIs it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,生命之火的点燃 思想和灵魂的诞生\NConception, that spark, the animation of thought and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,掌握在上帝的手中\NThat is in God's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而死亡\NBut death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,挑战正在此处\NAh, now there lies the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡应该掌握在我们手中\NThat should be our concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,应该如此\NIt should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们凭什么能掌控？ 我们又不是神明 对不对？\NWho are we to do so? We are not gods, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是我们能像神明那般大胆\NBut if we are to behave as immodestly as gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那至少能够创造奇迹\Nwe must, at the very least, deliver miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是？\NWouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在年轻学子心中点燃神圣火花\NIgnite a divine spark…in these young students' minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,教导他们抛弃顺从 违抗权威\NTeach them defiance rather than obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,展示人类有可能掌控自然奥秘 让死亡不再发生\NShow that man may pursue nature to her hiding places and stop death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是延缓死亡 而是长生不老！\NNot slow it down, but stop it entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,安静！\NSilence. Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这种不可能的事 你究竟要怎么教？\NHow exactly do you propose to teach what is impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的尸体 一个复合实体\NComposite subject, the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是某个店老板 刚咽气没多久就送到了我这里\NThat of a shopkeeper, delivered mere moments after expiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大脑暴露在外 但仍能运作\NThe brain laid bare but functional,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,脊神经分支和迷走神经完好无损\Nthe spinal branches and vagal nerves intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家或许能看到一些极细的伤口\NYou may observe the hair-thin scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手艺无需粗糙的缝合\NNo coarse stitching needed by my own technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看这条手臂\NThe arm, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,来自某个木匠\Ncomes from another specimen, that of a carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,肌肉、韧带、神经 都已连结好\NThe muscles, ligaments, nerves, all connected now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊 电流导致躯体痉挛\NNow, the spasmodic movement of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这已不是新鲜事\Ncaused from the electric current, this is not new.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都见过 不过 这种躯体内的能量流动\NIt's not new. However, the flow of energy through the body
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,遵循一种完全不同的概念\Nfollows a different notion entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一种称为气的东方概念\NAn Eastern notion called qi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.91,0:23:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这种概念认为 生命能量的流动 同时存在于身体内外\NNow, it considers the vital flow of energy both within and without.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我用针在六个…\NI'm utilizing needles in six--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,安静！都坐下！\NQuiet! Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,医生 这是听证会 不是狂欢节表演\NThis is a hearing, Doctor, not a carnival act.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样无济于事 维克多\NYou're not helping your cause, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这种用电的诡计根本没用\NThis galvanic trickery will simply not do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,诡计\NTrickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,诡计？\NTrickery?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗？\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是诡计 而是一种抉择\NThat is not trickery. That is a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一个死人的眼睛 和另一个死人的胳膊协调运动\NMotor coordination between the eye of one dead man and the arm of another,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,注入全新的意志和基本的理解力\Ninfused with a new will and the rudiments of understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,已经死亡的大脑也有理解力吗？\NUnderstanding in a brain that already died?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.54,0:24:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,放开\NRelease now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.04,0:24:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,请放开\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.45,0:24:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,礼貌一点总有效果\N"Please" always helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧关了吧 你个江湖骗子\NTurn that off at once. At once, you charlatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.25,0:24:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是未来 这是有可能实现的\NThis is the future. This is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.20,0:24:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不研究一下 量化一下呢？\NWhy not study it? Why not quantify it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.37,0:24:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是罪恶的 可恨、下流！\NThis is unholy. An abomination. An obscenity!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.16,0:24:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,生命由上帝赐予 由上帝收回 维克多\NGod gives life, and God takes it, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.00,0:24:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或许上帝就是无能！\NPerhaps God is inept!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.91,0:25:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要由我们来纠正他的错误！\NAnd it is we that must amend his mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.41,0:25:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别让这些老蠢货阻止你自由表达！\NDo not let these old fools extinguish your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.04,0:25:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只有采取不盲从的态度 摆脱恐惧和恃强凌弱的教条\NThe answers only come when coaxed by disobedience,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.50,0:25:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,答案才会浮现！\Nfree of fear and cowardly dogma!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.87,0:25:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,克伦佩教授\NProfessor Krempe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.04,0:26:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰肯斯坦男爵 我叫海因里希·哈兰德\NBaron Frankenstein, my name is Heinrich Harlander,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.95,0:26:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里有一封\Nand I carry with me a letter of introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.79,0:26:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你的弟弟威廉写的介绍信\Nfrom your brother, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.25,0:26:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟？\NFrom my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.29,0:26:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望能有幸认识你\NI asked for the privilege of your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.75,0:26:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,耽误你一点时间\NIt won't take but a minute of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.70,0:26:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-请进 -好\N-Please. -Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.58,0:26:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说 威廉要来看我 对吗？\NSo William is coming to see me, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.45,0:26:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对 几天后到\NYeah, in a matter of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.87,0:26:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让你见见他的未婚妻 也就是我的侄女\NHe wants to introduce you to his fiancée. My niece, as it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.41,0:26:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫伊丽莎白·哈兰德 是一位非常可爱的小姐\NElizabeth Harlander, a very nice young lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.29,0:26:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚从修道院学校毕业\Nfresh from convent life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.41,0:26:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这些照片都是我拍的\NThe photographs are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.91,0:26:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉在金融领域很有成就\NWilliam has become quite successful in the world of finance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰肯斯坦的名声越来越响了\NHe's making a name for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.91,0:26:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟！是吗？\NHa! A name? For himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.50,0:26:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道我们都是弗兰肯斯坦 不管我们乐不乐意\NWell, I'm afraid we both share that name, whether we like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.12,0:26:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我拜读了你在《柳叶刀》上的文章\NI read your article in The Lancet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.37,0:26:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得这事能做到吗？\NYou really believe you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.29,0:26:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,组装出一个人来？\NAssemble a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.58,0:27:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,做出完整的全新人体？还要有生命？\NA full new body? And give it life?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.79,0:27:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天也看到了\NYou saw it today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.29,0:27:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 我看到的是你当众受难\NWhat I saw was a crucifixion, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.70,0:27:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没开口说句话 就被钉死了\NYou were done for before you uttered a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.41,0:27:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是向他们展示了\NI still showed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.87,0:27:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,展示什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.79,0:27:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,事实\NThe truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.41,0:27:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到晚餐时间就忘了\NThey will forget by suppertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.50,0:27:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此 你觉得怎么样？\NYes, yes, yes. But what did you think? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.04,0:27:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得非常厉害\NI thought it was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.08,0:27:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我就知道\NIt was. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.25,0:27:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但你有点孩子气 太激动了\NBut you are like a child, so excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.12,0:27:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,紧抓你的新宠物 快把它勒死了\Nclutching your new pet so tightly that you're strangling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.50,0:27:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不免为你担心\NThat is why I worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.70,0:27:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你能控制好火种吗 普罗米修斯？\NCan you contain your fire, Prometheus?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.25,0:27:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没等把它交出去 就先烧伤了自己的手？\NOr are you going to burn your hands before delivering it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.54,0:27:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对\NQuite.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.41,0:27:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要觉得我无礼 但这一天已经足够漫长\NPlease do not think me rude, but my day has proven long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的状态也完全不适合 再陪伴陌生人了\Nand I believe myself totally unfit for the company of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.12,0:27:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有什么别的事了…\NSo if there's nothing more--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.70,0:27:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有重要的事\NOh, but there is. Much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.20,0:28:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我在爱丁堡找好了住处\NI've taken quarters in Edinburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.75,0:28:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,三天后 我们一起见威廉和伊丽莎白\NThree days from now, we are to meet with William and Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.25,0:28:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我将在那晚改变你的命运\NAnd that evening, I will change your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.70,0:28:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给你看些非同凡响的东西\NI will show you something extraordinary.
Comment: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{路人台词，仅中文，不重要 忽略}-你真好 -谢谢 给
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.41,0:28:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子 把桃子转过来\NThe peach. The peach. Turn the peach. Turn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.70,0:28:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你又啃了\NYou bit it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.33,0:28:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在吃桃\NYou're eating the peaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.50,0:28:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是对死亡的沉思\NThis is a memento mori.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.04,0:28:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子是生命和青春的符号 怎么就被你啃了？\NThe peach, symbol of life and youth, and you bite into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.50,0:28:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-我饿了呀 小希 -别那样叫我\N-I was hungry, Kiki. -Don't call me Kiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.79,0:28:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 维克多·弗兰肯斯坦男爵来了\NBaron Victor Frankenstein, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.04,0:28:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以下去了\NYou can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.66,0:28:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NForgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.33,0:29:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎\NWelcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.29,0:29:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哈兰德先生\NHerr Harlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.20,0:29:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种新兴艺术 摄影\NA young art, photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.95,0:29:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 小希\NGoodbye, Kiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.41,0:29:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经迷上了\NAlready a passion of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.75,0:29:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,文件都带来了吗？\NDid you bring the papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.54,0:29:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NOh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.20,0:29:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-你非常出色 -谢谢\N-You're extraordinary. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.58,0:29:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.37,0:29:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你利用神经系统来传递能量脉冲\NYou're using the nervous system to deliver the surge of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.70,0:29:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗？\NAre you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.75,0:29:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NCorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.00,0:29:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 你所操控的生命力 只能维持很短时间\NAnd thus the sustainability of the life force you command
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.08,0:29:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就会衰退、消散\Nis very brief, wanes, evaporates.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.00,0:29:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么说？\NHow so?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当时你颇为自豪地结束了演示\NAt the lecture, you ended your demonstration out of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.41,0:29:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实是因为 那股电流般的生命力\NBut really, because the galvanic life force
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.75,0:29:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,已经衰竭了 对吗？\Nwas already fading, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.58,0:29:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 你是外科医生吗？\NAre you yourself a surgeon, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.70,0:30:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经是 我是战地医生\NYeah, once upon a time. An army surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.12,0:30:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,医术也说不上多精湛\NNot a particularly skilled one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.79,0:30:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但也给我打下了发家致富的基础\NBut it allowed me to secure the rudiments of my fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.04,0:30:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在有几家军火工厂\NI own a few ammunition factories.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.04,0:30:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是军火商 -不如说是个务实的\N-An arms merchant. -A realist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.45,0:30:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你对伊夫林解剖图表熟悉吗？\NAre you familiar with the Evelyn Tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.41,0:30:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 那是约翰·伊夫林爵士当年\NOf course. Acquired by Sir John Evelyn,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.04,0:30:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,买下的四张人体标本精细解剖图\Nthere are four planks, meticulous dissection,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.08,0:30:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是欧洲最早的人体神经 和动静脉解剖图\Nsome of the oldest in Europe, presenting the nerves,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.20,0:30:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会提到这个？\Nveins and arteries of cadavers. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.16,0:30:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为还有第五张\NYes. But there's a fifth one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.91,0:30:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这张最让人信服\NThe most compelling one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.33,0:30:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,非常细致 是不是？\NExquisite, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.50,0:30:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,呈现于木头上的鲜活血肉\NFlesh rendered onto wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.29,0:30:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体放在木板上 逐层剥离\NThe cadaver lies on the plank, is peeled away layer by layer,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.66,0:30:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,用树脂将剩下的组织固定在木板上\Nand the remaining tissue is lacquered with resin onto the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.45,0:30:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是淋巴系统 -没错\N-It showcases the lymphatic system. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.83,0:30:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,穆斯林医学家称其为隐秘的循环系统\NMuslim medics called it the secret circulatory system.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.70,0:30:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅输送三升体液 却构成了庞大的网络\NIt moves a mere three liters of fluid, but it's a vast network.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.29,0:31:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-真是非同凡响 -确实\N-Oh, it's remarkable. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.16,0:31:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在对我们 也是对你而言 关键的改变就在这里\NNow for us, for you, the important variation is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.62,0:31:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这第九种构造 环绕心脏的结构\NThe ninth configuration. A very delicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.37,0:31:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,极为精巧 近乎空灵\Nalmost ethereal structure surrounding the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.83,0:31:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,既能分配能量 也能储存能量\NIt can distribute, but also store energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.79,0:31:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能在不破坏周围组织的前提下\NYes, if you can access that without destroying
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.33,0:31:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-触达这一构造… -不 不是前面\N-the surrounding tissue-- -No. Not through the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.95,0:31:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是后面 脊柱 胸曲\NThe back, spinal column, thoracic curvature.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.95,0:31:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.91,0:31:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,远超人们想象的能量流动 瘢痕形成和组织再生\NFlow of energy, scarring and regeneration beyond anyone's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.41,0:31:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,永生\NLife eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.70,0:31:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我将提供无限的资源 来支持你的研究\NI will endow your pursuit with unlimited resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.79,0:31:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要拿什么来交换？\NAnd in exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.75,0:31:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说就俗了\NNo need to become indelicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.25,0:31:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们探寻真理 志在超越 有着共同的追求\NWe're searchers for truth and transcendence, kindred spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.41,0:31:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,某天我也许会请你帮个忙 作为回报\NI may in time ask you for a favor in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.45,0:32:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但最重要的是记录研究过程 以传诸后世的这份特权\Nbut it's mostly the privilege to record your process for posterity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.54,0:32:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我习惯独自工作\NI work alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对不出声\NI'm very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.25,0:32:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哈兰德先生 威廉·弗兰肯斯坦和您的侄女到了\NWilliam Frankenstein and your niece, Herr Harlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.08,0:32:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要考虑一下\NI shall consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.54,0:32:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我会考虑的\NI'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.95,0:32:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,男爵\NBaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.12,0:32:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别假装冷静了 错过了就可惜了\NDon't pretend to be reasonable now. It would be such a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.62,0:32:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.04,0:32:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉！\NWilliam!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.25,0:32:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-维克多 -瞧瞧你\N-Victor. -Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.95,0:32:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 你长大了\NMy, you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.70,0:32:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜不是我的功劳\NThrough no merit of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.04,0:32:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来见见我的未婚妻吧\NMay I introduce the woman I'm to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.70,0:32:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白·哈兰德小姐\NLady Elizabeth Harlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.70,0:33:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,荣幸之至\NAbsolutely delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.95,0:33:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,听到你被驱逐 说实话我也不惊讶\NCan't say I was shocked when you were expelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.87,0:33:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们的态度太强硬 言语太狠毒\Nbut the manner and virulence of your expulsion,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.54,0:33:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为实在没有必要\Nuncalled for, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.79,0:33:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要\NNo, it was called for. 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我应得的\NI earned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.50,0:33:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我特意挣来的 你说是不是 哈兰德先生？\NI made it a point to earn it, wouldn't you say, Herr Harlander?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.08,0:33:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,确实声势浩大\NIt was quite an exit, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.33,0:33:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要激怒他们？\NWhy provoke them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.50,0:33:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,何不继续做自己的事 避免惹来不必要的关注？\NWhy not just carry on without calling attention to yourself in such a manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.95,0:33:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉 就算以你的标准来看 这么做也太保守了\NHow safe, even by your standards, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.70,0:33:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你这话听着都有点像父亲了\NYou almost sound like Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.66,0:33:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲可是相当老练的\NHe was a most tactful man, our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.20,0:33:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他做事精准、谨慎、有分寸感\NHe was precise, discreet, measured.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.91,0:33:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不是 我完全不懂为何谦虚是一种美德\NI, on the other hand, fail to see why modesty is considered a virtue at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.45,0:33:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多一直这么引人注目\NVictor's always been one to harvest attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.33,0:34:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,即便在小时候 我也常常 通过保持沉默 来消解他的声音\NEven as children, I mitigated his voice by staying silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.70,0:34:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的事发生无数次了吧 维克多 你说呢？\NPerhaps too much and far too many times, wouldn't you say, Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.66,0:34:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以再造生命\NIf life can be regenerated,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.95,0:34:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,并非简单的模拟\Nnot as a mere simulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.29,0:34:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而是通过物理化学手段 如神迹般地再造 何不大声说出来？\Nbut as a divine act by physical, chemical means, why whisper it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.00,0:34:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你笑了？\NYou laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.37,0:34:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你觉得好笑吗？ -没错\N-You're amused? -I must be, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.79,0:34:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的理念没表达清楚吗？\NAre my ideas not clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.20,0:34:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你显然已经够大声的了\NYou certainly expressed them loudly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.75,0:34:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不值得为之努力吗？\NAre they not worthwhile?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.08,0:34:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为理念本身并不值得为之努力\NIdeas are not worthwhile by themselves, I don't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.25,0:34:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,愿闻其详\NEnlighten me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.16,0:34:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,拿战争来说\NTake the war, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.45,0:34:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉 去书房享用雪茄和白兰地吧\NWilliam, cigar and brandy in my study?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.58,0:34:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我侄女的长篇大论你肯定都听过了\NSurely you've heard my niece expound on the matter before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.41,0:34:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失陪了\NYou'll excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.29,0:34:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,请继续说 关于理念\NPray, carry on. Ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.45,0:34:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说吧 荣耀、国家、勇气\NWell… honor, country, valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.62,0:35:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这些必然是值得为之奋斗的崇高理念\NThese surely are worthwhile, elevated ideas by themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.79,0:35:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,同意吧？\Nwouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.29,0:35:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 人们为了这些理念赴死\N-Mm-hmm. -And nevertheless, men are dying for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.04,0:35:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以一种显然毫不崇高的方式\NIn a decidedly un-elevated way,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.04,0:35:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,脸埋在泥泞里 喉咙呛着血\Nface down in the mud, choking on blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.00,0:35:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,痛得大喊大叫\Nscreaming in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.04,0:35:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是某人的父亲、兄弟或儿子\NMen that were fathers, brothers or sons to someone out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.45,0:35:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们被自己的母亲带到这个世界\NMen that were fed, cleaned and nursed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.45,0:35:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,被悉心喂养、洗净、照料、教育\Nand schooled into this world by their mothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.91,0:35:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,最后却被送到某个遥远的战场\Nonly to fall on a battlefield far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.95,0:35:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真正制造惨剧的人却躲得远远的\Nfar from those that provoke these tragedies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.37,0:35:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们好好地待在家中 不沾血 不挨刀\NThose men remain at home, untouched by blood or bayonet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.41,0:35:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,皮肤完好无损 被窝温暖洁净\Ntheir skin unpierced, their blankets warm and clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.12,0:35:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是蠢人追求理念的后果\NThat is what happens when ideas are pursued by fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.95,0:35:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那你觉得我是蠢人\NAnd you think me a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.54,0:35:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.33,0:35:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快享用你的白兰地和雪茄去吧\NRun to your brandy and cigars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.58,0:35:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都在等着呢\NThe boys are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.33,0:36:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人常常以为遇见了天使或魔鬼\NHow often a man believes he's met an angel or a devil,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.66,0:36:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来却发现一切不过是幻觉\Nonly to find it is all an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.95,0:36:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下的这盘棋\NThe game of chess we play…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.91,0:36:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对手只有自己\Nwe play only against ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.16,0:36:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮他\NHelp him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.62,0:36:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！\NHelp him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.66,0:36:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,给 喝点吧\NHere you go. Drink some.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.20,0:36:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟我来\NYou better come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.87,0:36:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.29,0:36:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 看守人看到他了\NSir, the watchman saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.79,0:36:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在迷雾中绕着船转\NCircling the ship. In the mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.54,0:36:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都亲眼看他沉下去了\NWe all saw him drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.25,0:36:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.50,0:36:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很恐慌\NThe men are terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.08,0:36:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得该把那个男人扔到冰面上\NThey think that man should be surrendered to the ice
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.54,0:36:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,结束这一切\Nand be done with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.33,0:37:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他受我保护…\NHe is under my protection…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.45,0:37:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,受王国庇佑！\Nand the protection of the Crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.83,0:37:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,几周后 我、威廉和哈兰德 骑马穿过海峡\NA few weeks later, I rode with William and Harlander
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.87,0:37:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,来到瓦杜兹附近的一个湖边\Nto a lake near Vaduz across the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.54,0:37:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这座塔楼是用来过滤农田灌溉用水的\NThe tower was built as a water filtration plant to irrigate the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.04,0:37:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是个公共工程项目 所以战争一开始就被弃建了\NPublic works, so construction was abandoned at the start of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.08,0:37:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这场战争 是前一场\NNot this war, the one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.54,0:37:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是再前面一场 我记不清了\NOr the one before that, I cannot quite remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.50,0:37:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一看到它\NThe moment I laid eyes on it…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.62,0:37:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这座塔楼\NThe tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.37,0:37:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我便感受到了命运的召唤\NI could feel destiny calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.79,0:38:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,建筑结构基本完整\NThe structure's basically intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.66,0:38:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还有一条陡坡道 从顶上直通到底部\NAnd there's a chute going from top, right to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.41,0:38:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我会安排人把你的个人物品\NI can arrange for your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.29,0:38:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,从爱丁堡运过来\NWe'll bring them from Edinburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.95,0:38:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么 都能满足\NAnything you need or want shall be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.54,0:38:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么都可以？ -什么都可以\N-Anything? -Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.83,0:38:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,整个项目期间 威廉随叫随到\NI have secured William's service for the duration of the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.45,0:38:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我要一个临时密室\NI'll need a holding cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.58,0:38:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-实验室旁边要有个冷库 -威廉\N-And an ice chamber close to the lab. -William.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.41,0:38:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,塔楼底部有两个泵水库\NThere are two pump reservoirs at the base of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.87,0:38:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要改造一下\NWe'll repurpose those.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.37,0:38:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要重启蒸汽机\NWe shall need to recondition the steam engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.37,0:38:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,需要足够的燃料 来保证机器正常运转\NWe'll need enough fuel to make sure they run.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.75,0:39:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那里 还有那里 放四块高容量的伏打电池\NThere and there, four high-capacity voltaic batteries,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正负电极\Npositive and negative polarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.25,0:39:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还要一套纯银避雷针系统 向下延伸至实验室\Nand a lightning rod system of pure silver telescoping down into the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.54,0:39:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 你需要什么设备 我的承包商都能造出来\NYes. My contractors can manufacture any and all equipment you may require.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.50,0:39:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我们应该达成共识了吧？\NI take it then that we have an understanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.20,0:39:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,交易达成\NA bargain has been struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.37,0:39:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋！\NBastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.08,0:39:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不行\NNo. No. Not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.33,0:39:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,张嘴\NAah. Open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.41,0:39:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被绞死算你走运 你本就活不过今年了\NYou, you're lucky to be hanged. You would have died within the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.62,0:39:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈兰德先生答应我 让我拿到最好的样本\NHerr Harlander promised me access to optimal specimens.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.20,0:39:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,阁下 他倒是答应了\NYeah, that he may have, your lordship,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.95,0:39:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可您也知道\Nbut as you well know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.37,0:40:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,犯罪又不是什么好差事 我们这里也只有些歪瓜裂枣\Ncrime doesn't pay, and it's a poor showing of it we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.95,0:40:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个都是可怜虫\NThey're wretches every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.79,0:40:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉\NI'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.50,0:40:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,背很强壮 这个可以\NThat's a strong back. This one will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.25,0:40:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,稍后再来\NCome back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.37,0:40:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,来告解？\NConfession?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.12,0:40:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好奇\NI was intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.45,0:40:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如此纤弱又虔诚的人 能有什么要告解的？\NWhat would such a delicate, pious creature have to confess to?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.12,0:41:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是碰巧 被我找到了一个机会\NAs luck would have it, an opportunity presented itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.62,0:41:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\Nand I…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.95,0:41:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要揭开谜底了\NI was about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.87,0:41:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,神父 请为我祝福 我有罪\NBless me, Father, for I have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.58,0:41:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子 你多久没告解了？\NHow long has it been since your last confession, my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.33,0:41:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还没到一周 神父 我在修道院待过\NBarely a week, Father. I was in a convent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.04,0:41:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就一周？\NA week?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.45,0:41:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么轻率地犯错了？\NTsk-tsk. Have you so hastily committed sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.66,0:41:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NI have.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.08,0:41:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是罪孽的念头 并非实际行动\NSin of intent, not deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.62,0:41:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-因为一名男子 对不对？ -对\N-A man, is it? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.70,0:41:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是我未婚夫的兄长\NMy fiancé's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.50,0:41:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是欲念吗？\NLust?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.75,0:41:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是憎恶\NHatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.66,0:41:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恶…\NHatred…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.45,0:41:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-憎恶？ -那名男子很恶劣、很丑陋\N-Hatred? -The man is appalling, grotesque.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.79,0:41:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话很是刺耳\NHarsh words.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.37,0:42:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,近乎无情了 对吗？\NRather uncharitable, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.08,0:42:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,尊敬的神父 您并不了解这个人\NRespectfully, Father, you do not know this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.62,0:42:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他试图操控周围一切的人和事\NHe tries to control and manipulate everything and everyone around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.16,0:42:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他和所有暴君一样 以假扮受害者为乐\NLike every tyrant, he delights in playing the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.87,0:42:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要我说 那是他唯一的本事\NHis only advantage, I would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.37,0:42:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他自以为绅士 实则粗鄙不堪\Nis he's far cruder than he believes himself to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.87,0:42:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,粗鄙不堪？\NCruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.70,0:42:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子 请详细说明\NUh, pray explain yourself, my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.41,0:42:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说 他太容易被发现了\NFor one, he's easy to spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.00,0:42:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是集市日的拥挤街道上 也能轻松看到他\NYou can see him… even on a busy street on market day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.33,0:42:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧 你什么时候发现我的？\NTell me, how soon did you spot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.12,0:42:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只能说远比你看到我来得早\NI saw you well before you saw me, I can say that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.12,0:42:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃过晚饭了吗？\NHave you had supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.25,0:42:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不怎么饿 男爵 谢谢\NI'm not that hungry, Baron. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.08,0:42:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我就饿坏了\NWell, I for one am famished.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.45,0:42:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢 好心人 -谢谢 先生\N-Thank you, my good man. -Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.62,0:42:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你买了什么书？能让我看看吗？\NWhat books did you buy, hmm? May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.12,0:42:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜\NGuess.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.79,0:42:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-让我猜？ -还是猜一下吧\N-Guess? -Mm-hmm. I'd rather that you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.37,0:42:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那好\NVery well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.00,0:42:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,言情小说\NA romance…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.91,0:43:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沐浴着地中海的阳光 身着丝绸华服 沉醉于爱的纠葛\Ndrenched in Mediterranean sun and silk and the skirmishes of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.25,0:43:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是无礼 但也不奇怪\NInsulting, but unsurprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.79,0:43:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.04,0:43:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,昆虫？\N-Insects? -Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.66,0:43:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我对科学的兴趣 体现在对微小生物的好奇上\NMy interest in science leans towards the smallest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.20,0:43:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,它们随自然而动 或许是顺应上帝的节律\NMoving with nature, perhaps the rhythms of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.20,0:43:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在寻觅 某种更纯粹、更奇妙的事物\NI've always searched for something more pure, marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.00,0:43:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你在修道院追寻的东西吗？\NIs that what you were seeking in the convent?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.91,0:43:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧\NIn a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.12,0:43:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,值得吗？\NWas it worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.95,0:43:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么是值得的吗？\NIs anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.12,0:43:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？\NPermit me, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.20,0:44:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好像不大合适\NThis hardly seems appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.20,0:44:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么是合适的吗？\NIs anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.83,0:44:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NVery well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.37,0:44:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,笑起来！\NLaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.00,0:44:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,生平第一次\NAnd for the very first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.50,0:44:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不知何故 我对生的兴趣渐浓\NI became more interested in life
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.20,0:44:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对死的兴趣\Nand somewhat less interested
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.04,0:44:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,减淡了\N in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.87,0:44:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,主杆采用快速螺栓固定系统\NThe main rod has a fast bolting system.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.00,0:44:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,用合金了吗？\NDid you use an alloy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.33,0:44:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,铜锌合金\NCopper and zinc.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.95,0:45:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不行 重来吧\NThis is… This simply will not do. Start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.54,0:45:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,纯银是完美的导体\NPure silver is a perfect conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.91,0:45:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉 你得留下 拜托了\NWilliam, you must stay behind. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.20,0:45:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我最信任的就是你了\NI trust you above anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.20,0:45:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再多待几天就行\NOnly for a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.25,0:45:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你抓不到它的\NYou're not going to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.83,0:45:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮\NBeautiful. Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.58,0:45:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,把它关起来 还是放走呢？\N-Should we trap her or let her go? -Mm…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.91,0:45:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,关起来\NTrap her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.37,0:45:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我们有共同点了\NNow we have something in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.79,0:45:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一个囚徒\NA prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.29,0:45:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉如约行事 认真负责建造实验室 满足各种需求\NAs promised, William took dutiful charge of the laboratory build and needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.37,0:45:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那边能修一下吗？\NCan you fix that over there, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.50,0:45:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去帮一下\NGo, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.45,0:45:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他严格按我的指示办事\NHe followed my instructions to the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.66,0:45:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,电池\NThe battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.58,0:46:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是纯银的了\NIt's all pure silver now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.70,0:46:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是和淋巴系统相对应的传导点\NConduction points corresponding to the lymphatic system,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.25,0:46:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,非常复杂 但我做出来了\Nwhich was quite complex. -But I managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.33,0:46:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.79,0:47:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哈兰德先生 谢谢 派对很精彩\NHerr Harlander, thank you. The party's delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.08,0:47:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿我们没有干扰你做研究\NI hope we're not distracting you from your research
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.62,0:47:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟你还要顾着我和伊丽莎白\Nto tend to me and Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.54,0:47:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有\NNot at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.62,0:47:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她还年轻 我们得护着她\NShe's young. She can count on us to guard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.75,0:47:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是回避一下\NI shall leave you your privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.54,0:47:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之间还掩饰什么\NNo need for subterfuge between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.29,0:47:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,法国陶瓷 多么美妙的共响\NFrench porcelain, chimes to a man's stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.12,0:47:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我快找到解决方法了 给淋巴系统确定传导点\NI am very near a solution, an access point to the lymphatic system.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.45,0:47:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那个呀\NAh, yeah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.00,0:47:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这么久了\NIt's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.41,0:47:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,仗快打完了\NThe war is waning.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.04,0:47:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,资金供应也快断了\NAnd my funding will end with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.25,0:47:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说资金无限供应吗？\NYou said your funds were unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.79,0:47:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的耐心是有限的\NMy patience is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.04,0:47:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到了可靠消息 一周内会爆发一场战斗\NI have it on good authority that a battle is to take place within a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.79,0:48:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,战争好比潮水 会把战利品送到我们这条海岸上来\NThe tide of war will deliver its bounty to our shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.04,0:48:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,战场上的尸体肯定一塌糊涂\NA battlefield? The bodies will be mangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.29,0:48:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就一周\NOne week.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.12,0:48:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-一周？ -一周后 创造历史的机会就会溜走\N-One week? -After that, history will pass us by.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.66,0:48:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我冲一下吧 男爵\NFlush that for me, will you, Baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.58,0:48:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一周内找到传递电流的办法\NA week to determine how to deliver the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.45,0:48:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,绝无可能\NImpossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.58,0:48:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？\NWhat would I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.91,0:48:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就快成功了 我感觉得到\NI was close. I could feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.58,0:48:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知横生阻碍\NAnd then…life got in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.58,0:48:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.45,0:48:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它肯定想你了\NI believe she missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.25,0:48:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白 我得先警告你一下 我在处理解剖体\NI must warn you, Elizabeth, I've been working on a dissection.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.00,0:48:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很美\NIt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.83,0:48:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,吓到你了吗？\NDoes it shock you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.87,0:48:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想起了殉道主题的绘画\NReminds me of martyrdom paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.70,0:48:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了痛苦\NPain is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.20,0:48:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在对称的构造和形状中 看得到上帝的精妙手笔\NYou can see God's design in the symmetry and the shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.79,0:48:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白\NElizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.79,0:49:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我得向你坦白\NI must confess something to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.50,0:49:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信这世间存在奇妙非凡之物 你也一样\NI have a belief in the marvelous and so do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.62,0:49:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之间有种默契 你能感觉到吗？\NThere is a bond between us. Can you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.12,0:49:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一种近乎生理上的吸引 我坚信这种感觉绝非寻常\NAn almost physical one. I truly believe it to be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.04,0:49:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你所信之物 未必是事实\NBelieving something does not make it true.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.37,0:49:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么来这里？\NThen why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.16,0:49:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它很美 对不对？\NBeautiful creature, is she not?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.08,0:49:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,孤傲 令人沉迷 却又如此怪异\NRemote. Entirely bewitching, but so odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.08,0:49:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有三颗心\NThree hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.12,0:49:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,复眼 白色的血\NMultiple eyes. White blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.00,0:50:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,它无法做出选择 所以如此迷人\NAnd a fascinating lack of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.95,0:50:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.45,0:50:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有选择的能力 灵魂才能栖息\NChoice is the seat of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.04,0:50:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是上帝对我们的赠礼\NThe one gift God granted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.12,0:50:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白\NElizabeth…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.54,0:50:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我做出选择了\NI have chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.04,0:50:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.79,0:50:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白！\NElizabeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.04,0:50:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白！\NElizabeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.41,0:50:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我失败了\NI thought I had failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.25,0:50:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以为一切都完了 以为…\NI thought it was entirely over. I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.95,0:50:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为…\NAnd I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.16,0:50:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\NAnd I…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.95,0:50:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对称性\NThe symmetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.62,0:51:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝创造的对称性 对\NGod's symmetry. Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.12,0:51:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.25,0:51:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,把电池放在淋巴系统上\NPlacing the battery above the lymphatic system.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.16,0:51:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我就这么找到了解题的关键\NI had found the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.66,0:51:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再也没有什么能阻挡我了\NNothing could stop me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.62,0:51:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.41,0:51:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！这堆尸体\NNo! No, do not take any bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.62,0:51:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,顶上的和底部的都别搬 就搬我做了标记的\Nfrom the top or the bottom of the pile unless I mark them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.87,0:51:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,冰冻或腐败可能会破坏组织\NIce or rot may have destroyed the tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.95,0:51:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就看中间的那些\NLook only in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.75,0:52:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,东西太多 会让人晕头转向 除非目标非常明确\NAbundance can be disorienting unless one hones one's aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.70,0:52:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要个子高的 长手长脚的\NI'm favoring tall specimens, long limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.54,0:52:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,划定范围 活就好干了\NScale will make the work easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.37,0:52:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢\NI like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.33,0:52:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,尽善尽美嘛\NPerfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.37,0:52:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不好呢 亲爱的男爵？\NAnd why not, dear Baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.79,0:52:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 有什么不好呢？\NIndeed, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.83,0:52:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,找到完整的人头\NLook for a head that's intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.79,0:52:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,搬到车上去\NPut that one in the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.16,0:52:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个放那边\NSet that one over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.87,0:52:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的送过来\NBring the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.95,0:52:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\NOh, good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.79,0:53:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,劳驾\NDo you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.25,0:55:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大功告成\NIt is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.62,0:56:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哈兰德先生！\NHerr Harlander!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.91,0:56:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雨要来了！\NA storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.04,0:56:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的拐杖\NMy cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.37,0:56:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的拐杖！\NMy cane!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.79,0:56:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的拐杖 手柄打开\NMy cane, in the handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.79,0:56:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,水银\NMercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.79,0:56:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-你病了吗？ -谢谢\N-Are you ill? -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.54,0:56:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是梅毒吗？\NIs it… syphilis?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.37,0:56:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我快死了\NYeah, I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.70,0:56:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一夜偷欢 终生服毒\NOne night with Venus, a lifetime with Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.79,0:56:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么说的吧？\NIsn't that the phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.66,0:56:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,几期了？\NWhat stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.79,0:56:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,二期？\NSecondary?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.70,0:56:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都清楚会怎么发展\NWe both know the precise schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.33,0:57:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,已经在啃噬我的骨头了\NIt starts to eat away my bones,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.70,0:57:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,眼眶、脸颊、牙齿、下颌、颅骨 层层侵蚀 直到抵达大脑\Norbital, cheek, teeth, jaw, skull, exposing my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.41,0:57:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,长瘤、发狂、剧痛\NTumors, madness, excruciating pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.37,0:57:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到某个清晨 我会开始尖叫 停不下来\NOne fine morning, I will start to scream and I will never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.83,0:57:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法接受如此不堪地死去\NI cannot face such a vulgar demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.45,0:57:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我想到了我唯一的要求\NWhich brings me to my one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.25,0:57:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们约定好的交易\NOur deal. As agreed, in exchange
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.29,0:57:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你慷慨解囊所能换取的东西\Nfor my generous intervention on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.45,0:57:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我们即将造出新人类\NAnd as we give life to our new Adam,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.37,0:57:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要拥有这具完美新身体\NI want to be placed in this new perfect body.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.37,0:57:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.41,0:57:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-不可以 -当然可以\N-No, no. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.04,0:57:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还没到时候！\NNot now. Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.00,0:57:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-正是这时候 -这事我们以后再聊 现在不行\N-Precisely now. -We'll talk about this after, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.00,0:57:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哪还有什么以后！\NThere is no after!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.83,0:57:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有以后了\NThere is no after.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.04,0:58:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要的一切 我都给你了！\NI gave you everything you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.12,0:58:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你要什么 我都给你\NI give you everything you ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.37,0:58:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,随你说\NName it, it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.87,0:58:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要伊丽莎白都行\NEven Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.04,0:58:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.20,0:58:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,礼貌一点总有效果\N"Please" always helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.75,0:58:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经病入膏肓了\NThe disease has spread all inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.54,0:58:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是全身性疾病 你知道的\NIt's systemic, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.75,0:59:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你的每个器官都感染了\NEvery organ in you is polluted.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.79,0:59:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大脑 血液 全都感染了\NYour brain, your blood, it's all polluted.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.95,0:59:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还有钱啊 对不对？\NBut my money's not, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.58,0:59:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,无济于事\NIt's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.41,0:59:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要你说一个“行”字\NNow, all you need to say is one simple word.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.79,0:59:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别的什么都不要说\N"Yes," no more and no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.62,0:59:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！听明白了吗？不行！\NNo! Do you understand? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.20,0:59:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.83,0:59:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.50,0:59:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.58,0:59:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没了这个 我们就一无所有了 我们俩都会完蛋\NIf we lose that, we have nothing. We both lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.04,0:59:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,普罗米修斯 我就是啄食你肝脏的鹰！\NI will be the eagle that feasts on your liver!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.83,0:59:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 住手！\NPlease, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.41,0:59:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哈兰德先生！\NHerr Harlander. Herr Harlander!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.04,0:59:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 看着我！\NHold on, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.20,0:59:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不！哈兰德先生\NNo! Herr Harlander!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.70,1:00:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊\NNo, no. No!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.75,1:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.70,1:02:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.37,1:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.58,1:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗了我\NYou lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.33,1:02:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,骗了我\NYou lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.33,1:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.75,1:02:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.41,1:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来 求你了\NNo, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.12,1:04:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看 一样的\NLook. Same.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.08,1:04:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳\NSun.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.08,1:04:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光\NSun. Light.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.33,1:04:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,去感受一下\NFace it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.04,1:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光 太阳…\NSunlight. The sun is…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.33,1:04:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳是生命之源\NThe sun is life.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.41,1:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很温暖\NAh, the warmth. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.54,1:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes! Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.70,1:04:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.87,1:04:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.70,1:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-维克多 -对\N-Victor. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.08,1:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对 你就是\NYes, yes, yes. Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.37,1:04:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然就是\NOf course you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.00,1:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.50,1:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,邮件来了\NThe mail, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.04,1:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老庄园来的信\NLetters from the old estate.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.00,1:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,日内瓦\NGeneva.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.83,1:05:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-有我叔叔的来信吗？ -没有\N-Is there anything from my uncle? -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.16,1:05:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我们该去拜访一下他们了\NPerhaps we should pay them a visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.37,1:05:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 看着脚下\NCareful. Look. Look down.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.33,1:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,水\NWater. Water.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.91,1:05:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,水\NWater.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.95,1:05:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对 水\NYes, water.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.75,1:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-维克多 -不 我是维克多\N-Victor. -No, I'm Victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.16,1:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是水 来这里\NThat's water. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.58,1:05:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-维克多 -来吧 很好\N-Victor. -Come now, come. All right, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.41,1:05:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要跨一大步\NWe're going to take a big step.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.16,1:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起来 准备好了？\NWe'll do it together. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.50,1:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-走这边 这样 -维克多\NThis way, like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.83,1:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样 走这边\NNo, not like that. This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.66,1:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰 烫\NOh, no, no, no. Hot, hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.75,1:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不能碰 别碰它\NNo, don't touch. Don't touch that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.33,1:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,烫\NIt's hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.16,1:06:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下 很好 真棒\NSit. Very good. Very good. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.66,1:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好 看这是什么\NYes. Now, look what I have here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.00,1:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看这个 这是什么？\NLook at this. What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.83,1:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个怪东西是什么？当心\NWhat is this strange thing? Careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.33,1:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你力气很大\NYou're very strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.37,1:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 这样\NYes. And like this. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.50,1:06:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要那个？好 这个放这里\NYes, you want another? Yes, this one goes right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.29,1:06:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙\NKey.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.29,1:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.33,1:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你就不会着凉了\NThis will keep you nice and warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.29,1:06:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,披上一条好毯子 暖暖的\NNice blanket to keep you warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.54,1:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\N-Victor. 
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.16,1:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.54,1:06:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你待在这里\NYou stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.37,1:06:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就待在这里\NYou stay here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.54,1:06:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,待着别动\NStay here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.75,1:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我去去就回 待着别动\NI'll be back. All right. Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.33,1:06:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.45,1:06:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别动 没事的\NNo, no, no, no, no. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.08,1:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回来的\NI'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.00,1:07:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.50,1:07:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.45,1:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对他来说 一切都是新的\NEverything was new to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.50,1:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,温暖、冰冷、阳光、黑暗\NWarmth, cold, light, darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.54,1:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任务是塑造他\NAnd I was there to mold him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.08,1:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,造成之后的事 我还从未考虑过\NI never considered what would come after creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.70,1:07:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来到世界尽头\NAnd having reached the edge of the earth,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.12,1:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才发现没有地平线\Nthere was no horizon left.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.45,1:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如此成就有种非自然的感觉\NThe achievement felt unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.79,1:07:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,并无意义\NVoid of meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.58,1:07:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我十分烦恼\NAnd this troubled me so.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.66,1:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,船员们都想回去\NYour men, they wish to go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.00,1:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗？\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.45,1:07:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧\NProbably.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.70,1:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不过一旦船能开动 我们就会继续前行\NBut the moment we're free, we're setting sails forwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.16,1:07:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不管付出什么代价\NNo matter the cost.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.54,1:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你简直和我一样疯狂\NYou share my madness.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.91,1:08:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你讲述自己的故事 或许别有深意\NPerhaps there is a finer point in me telling you my story.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.25,1:08:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,男爵 不管是否如此\NWhether there is or isn't, Baron…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.12,1:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我都愿意听\NI'd like to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.45,1:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,几周过去了\NWeeks passed,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.37,1:08:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他的力量迅速增强 我却日渐衰弱\Nand as his strength increased rapidly, mine waned.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.70,1:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜他没学会更多的话 也没有别的进展\NAlas, no further language or development occurred.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.12,1:08:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不对\NNo, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.83,1:08:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,低头\NDown, down, down, down.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.62,1:08:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了\NYes, there we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.04,1:08:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了 别动\NThere we are. Stay there. Stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.20,1:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你\NYes, that's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.91,1:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你 知道了吗？\NThat's you. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.70,1:08:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,愈合得很好\NOh, yes, this is healing rather nicely.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.66,1:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我累了\NI'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.87,1:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我好久没睡了\NI have not slept.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.83,1:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都没睡\NNot a winky-dinky-doo of sleep for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.50,1:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在照顾你\NTending to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.91,1:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,终于给你脸上刮干净了\NI've finished shaving you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.66,1:09:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 别动\NNo, no, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.58,1:09:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,放下 不可以 松开\NLet go. No, no, no, no, no, no. Open.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.00,1:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,手松开 快松开\NOpen your hand. Open. Open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.12,1:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.16,1:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你都干了什么\NLook. Look what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.75,1:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你要听我的话 我说了放下\NYou have to listen to me. You have to listen. I said drop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.50,1:09:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真蠢！不 别这样\NStupidity! No. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.25,1:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.16,1:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-维克多 -不 别碰我！\N-Victor. -No, don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.66,1:09:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,永远都别碰我！\NDon't ever touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.12,1:09:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.16,1:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我 是你自己弄的\NI didn't do this. You did this.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.20,1:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口\NThe wound.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.54,1:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,闭合了\NIt's closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.25,1:09:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会的\NBut how?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.75,1:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.16,1:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\NNo, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.66,1:10:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.62,1:10:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.20,1:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NAll right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.66,1:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定一切都好\NI'm sure everything's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.08,1:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就到了\NWe'll be there soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.87,1:10:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你有想法 我知道\NI know you have thoughts. I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.87,1:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你有\NI know you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.12,1:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里面 你有想法\NSomewhere in there. Somewhere in there you have thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.79,1:10:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是？\NHmm? Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.45,1:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么吗？\NSomething you might want to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.87,1:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然脑子里很乱、很困惑\NHowever jumbled, however confused?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.79,1:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有想法吗？\NHmm? Something?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.41,1:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我太心急了？\NAm I presuming too much?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.62,1:10:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.75,1:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了！\NYes, yes, yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.87,1:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个已经教会你了\NThis much we have established.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.83,1:10:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的名字 我的名字是维克多\NThat is my name. My name is Victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.12,1:10:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能说点别的吗？什么都可以\NIs there anything else that you can say? Anything at all? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.70,1:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗？\NAnything? Anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.83,1:11:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳\NUm, sun, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.79,1:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,冷、雨、血 任何东西\NCold. Rain. Blood. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.00,1:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,靴子 靴子会说吗？\NBoot. Can you say "boot"?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.70,1:11:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.25,1:11:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,够了！那么…\NNo, yes, no, yes! How about…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.25,1:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,手呢？手会说吗？\NHow about "hand"? Can you say "hand"?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.04,1:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,手 说啊…\NHand. Hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.87,1:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是怕我吗？\NOh. Oh, oh. You are afraid of me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.62,1:11:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕我？\NYou're afraid of me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.33,1:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么你会怕我？\NWhy? Why would you be afraid of me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.66,1:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你的\NI'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.70,1:11:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你的 是我造了你\NI'm not going to hurt you. I made you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.00,1:11:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是我造了你！别这样了！\NI'm your maker! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.45,1:11:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来了 真的来了\NYou're here. You're really here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.16,1:12:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 快进来\NCome on, then. Come, come.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.41,1:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白 我得说 我有好多东西要给你看\NI have to tell you. I have so much to show you, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.00,1:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,特别奇妙 你都不敢相信\NYou won't believe it. It's absolutely marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.00,1:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快来 先给你看我的笔记\NCome, come, I'll show you my notes first.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.75,1:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔在这里吗？\NIs my uncle here?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.00,1:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.66,1:12:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔 他在这里吗？\NMy uncle, is he here?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.95,1:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不在\NNo, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.37,1:12:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就我一个人 他不在\NNo, I'm alone. He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.16,1:12:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-他…他几天后会回来 -维克多 你看着状态不大好\N-He's… He'll be back in a few days. -You don't look very well, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.08,1:12:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的状态从来没这么好过！ 我的头脑清晰多了！快来！\NOh, I've never felt better! I've never had a clearer mind! Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.33,1:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你发烧了吗？\NAre you running a fever?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.33,1:12:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是看到你太激动了\NI am just very excited to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.62,1:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我太高兴了 简直要飞起来了\NI'm exalted. The spirits have lifted me so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.08,1:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西太神奇了 我就知道能实现\NAbsolutely marvelous…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.79,1:12:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.33,1:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多 请给我一点时间\NVictor. Victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.50,1:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁伤害了你？\NWho hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.75,1:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉 你一定要看看这个\NI have to show you this, William.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.54,1:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我先整理一下\NLet me organize it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.12,1:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有东西要给你看\NAnd I have something to show to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.04,1:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟英国皇家医学会的人聊过了\NI've spoken to the Royal Medical Society.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.70,1:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们想见你 -现在还不行\N-They're interested in seeing you. -No, no, no, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.83,1:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没准备好\NI'm not quite ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.33,1:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为这是你一直以来的梦想\NI thought that's what you always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.41,1:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人\NThe man.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.50,1:15:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-楼下的那个男人 -你看到他了？\N-The man downstairs. -You saw him?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.91,1:15:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他是病人吗？是被你打伤的吗？\NIs he a patient? A victim?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.08,1:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他身上好多伤口 你竟然下手那么重\NHis wounds. You wounded him like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.29,1:15:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 伤害他的是这个世界 伊丽莎白\NNo, no, no. It was the world that hurt him, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.08,1:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我给了他生命\NI… I gave him life.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.41,1:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我给了他生命\NI gave him life.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.00,1:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,起来\NUp, up, up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.87,1:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.83,1:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着\NThere, there, there…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.33,1:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他还在适应周围的环境\NHe's still getting used to his surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.12,1:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它很强壮 威廉\NIt is strong, William.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.25,1:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你成功了 -非常强壮\N-You did it. -It's so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.79,1:15:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你成功了\NYou did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.33,1:15:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,体内所有系统都正常运作\NAll its systems are functional.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.37,1:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口都在愈合\NAll healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.79,1:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,愈合的状态不稳定\NAnd the healing is erratic, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.08,1:16:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是非同寻常\NBut exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.41,1:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么被拴在这里？\NWhy is he chained here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.20,1:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保护他自己 还有我\NFor his own safety and for mine,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.95,1:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也更方便给它清洁维护\Nand it's easy to clean and, uh, maintain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.70,1:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很多事它还不懂\NAnd it doesn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.50,1:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但你懂\NBut you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.70,1:16:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哈兰德知道了吗？\NDoes Harlander know?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.37,1:16:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在他回来之前把一切准备好…\NWe have to prepare everything for the moment he returns.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.08,1:16:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-当然 -…让一切都有模有样\N-Of course. -And have everything presentable.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.75,1:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它有智慧吗？\NIs it intelligent?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.37,1:16:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多 它有智慧吗？\NVictor, is it intelligent?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.62,1:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法理解你是怎么做到的\NI can't fathom how exactly you did what you did,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.83,1:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但这无疑是一项壮举\Nbut its dimension does not escape me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.29,1:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多 你有没有问过自己\NVictor, did you ever ask yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.04,1:17:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人的所有组成部分中\Nof all the parts that make that man,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.83,1:17:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哪块是灵魂藏身的地方？\Nwhich one holds the soul?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.45,1:17:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我没问过\NNo, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.58,1:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,楼下那头怪物总让人感到不安\NThere's something so disquieting about that creature down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.20,1:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,扭曲诡异 像个在哈哈镜里探头探脑的身影\NAskew, like a figure peeking around a funhouse mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.20,1:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但很有活力\NBut animated.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.29,1:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪里来的活力？\NAnimated by what?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.33,1:18:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,痛吗？\NDoes it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.50,1:18:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,叶子？\NA leaf?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.95,1:18:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,给我的吗？\NFor me?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.83,1:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.04,1:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很美？\NIsn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.87,1:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,给我的吗？\NThis is for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.58,1:19:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是伊丽莎白\NI'm Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.62,1:19:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,会说吗？伊丽莎白\NCan you say "Elizabeth"?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.29,1:19:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白\NElizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.62,1:19:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,从喉咙里发出声音\NMy throat makes sounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.75,1:19:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白\NElizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.75,1:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了\NI'm going to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.75,1:19:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎…白\NEliza… beth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.83,1:20:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不该靠近那东西的\NYou should not go near it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.66,1:20:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西？\N"It"?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.66,1:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 那东西\NIt. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.25,1:20:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西是活的 但没有智慧的火花\NI believe there is life in it, but not the spark of intelligence 
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.45,1:20:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我故意这么设计的\Nthat I had intended.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.54,1:20:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可能不是你想象的那样\NPerhaps not as you understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.25,1:20:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么地方出了差错\NSomething went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.95,1:20:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,阻塞了 缝合了 连通了\NA blockage, a suture, a connection.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.45,1:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伟大的维克多·弗兰肯斯坦 还会犯错？\NYou, the great Victor Frankenstein, you made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.04,1:20:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那头怪物只会一个词 仅有的一个\NThe Creature knows but one word, and one word alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.33,1:20:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\N"Victor, Victor, Victor, Victor."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.37,1:20:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是莫名其妙地机械重复\NIt just parrots it without rhyme or reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.95,1:20:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也许在当下 那个词就是他的一切\NPerhaps for the time being that word means everything to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.04,1:20:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要是重生后的他 获得活力的源泉其实更简单\NWhat if in being anew, the spirit that animates him is simpler,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.45,1:20:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-更纯粹… -纯粹？\N-purer-- -Purer?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.66,1:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,比普通人的更纯粹呢？\NPurer than that of the common man?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.29,1:20:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他不受制于原罪\NWhat if, unrestrained by sin,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.04,1:20:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而造物主为这具伤痕累累的血肉之躯 直接注入了生气呢？\Nour creator's breath came into its wounded flesh directly?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.95,1:20:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 伊丽莎白\NGood God, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.91,1:20:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我强迫自己信了你这话\NIf I could force myself to believe it,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.12,1:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我会觉得你是不是被这东西吸引了\Nit would be my inclination to see attraction in you for that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.25,1:20:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好好理解一下\NUnderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.62,1:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他的眼中有痛苦的情绪\NIn those eyes I saw pain,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.00,1:21:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有智慧 何来痛苦？\Nand what is pain if not evidence of intelligence?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.12,1:21:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那我的痛苦算什么？\NWhat about my pain?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.91,1:21:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,被你拒绝算什么？\NWhat about what you have denied me?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.91,1:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心想要什么？\NWhat my heart wants…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.87,1:21:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心？\NYour heart?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.33,1:21:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人体结构中\NOf all the human anatomy,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.75,1:21:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只有心最难捉摸\Nthat is the organ furthest from your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.33,1:21:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,男爵 只有怪物会扮演上帝\NOnly monsters play God, Baron.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.25,1:21:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,比普通人更纯粹\NPurer than the common man, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.54,1:21:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎的 我成了坏人\NAnd I, somehow, the villain. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.87,1:21:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心很纯粹？\NYour heart is pure?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.37,1:21:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 并非如此\NI assure you it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.41,1:21:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 因为是我亲手放进去的\NI should know. I put it there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.62,1:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,上去\NUp.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.79,1:22:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再试一下\NLet us try again.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.20,1:22:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,腿伸出来\NNow give me your leg.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.16,1:22:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,腿！\NLeg!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.50,1:22:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,腿伸出来！\NGive me your leg!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.37,1:22:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没有智慧 何来痛苦？\NPain is evidence of intelligence, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.33,1:22:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,行 测试一下这个说法吧\NWell, let's test the theory.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.62,1:22:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,腿伸出来！\NGive me your leg!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.20,1:22:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,腿！\NLeg!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.08,1:22:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,腿！\NLeg!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.08,1:22:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.95,1:22:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出来 你个野兽！\NGive it to me, you beast!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.83,1:22:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,腿伸出来！\NGive me your leg!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.04,1:22:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,腿！\NLeg!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.62,1:22:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.25,1:22:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.37,1:22:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.29,1:22:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor! Victor!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.91,1:22:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多 怎么了？\NWhat is it, Victor?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.29,1:22:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,来\NCome. Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.54,1:22:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我失败了 我犯了大错\NI failed. I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.66,1:22:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没有失败 我看过你的图纸了 -失败了\N-No, you didn't fail. I saw your papers. -I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.75,1:22:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-非常完美 -那头怪物极其危险\N-It's perfect. -The Creature is extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.87,1:23:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有…维克多\NThere's not… Victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.12,1:23:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等哈兰德回来 再一起讨论吧\NLet's wait for Harlander and discuss together.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.20,1:23:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉 有件事我得告诉你\NWilliam, there is something you should know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.33,1:23:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我得给你看一下\NSomething I have to show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.54,1:23:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈兰德… -那头怪物突然暴怒 把他杀了\N-Ha-- Harlander… -In a fit of rage, he killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.70,1:23:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这下你知道 我为什么没有及时告诉你了吧？\NDo you understand now why I was hesitant to share this with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.50,1:23:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,当然也不敢让伊丽莎白知道\NAnd certainly not with Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.83,1:23:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在怎么办？\NS… So what's to be done now?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.12,1:23:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.04,1:23:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在怎么办？ -你说怎么办？\N-What's to be done? -"What's to be done"?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.75,1:23:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你得带伊丽莎白回维也纳\NYou must take Elizabeth back to Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.54,1:23:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就说出了急事 必须马上走\NTell her something urgent came up and you have to leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.87,1:23:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别让她知道\NKeep her in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.54,1:23:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了保护她\NFor her own safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.16,1:23:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,必须照我说的办\NYou have to do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.66,1:23:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很快就回来 但现在只能先走\NWe'll be back in no time. But for now, this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.70,1:23:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请上马车吧\NNow get in the carriage, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.79,1:24:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得那头怪物能活多久？\NThe Creature, what's its lifespan, you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.91,1:24:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,必然没多久\NBrief. Very brief, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.37,1:25:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我有种很坏的预感\NI have the most terrible feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.16,1:25:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.66,1:25:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让马车回头\NTurn the carriage around.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.08,1:25:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人去维也纳吧\NYou go to Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.83,1:25:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让马车回头 否则我就跳车 他要杀了他\NTurn the carriage around or I will jump. He's going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.50,1:25:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,说个词吧\NSay one word.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.12,1:25:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一个 随便什么\NOne word more. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.58,1:25:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你说了 我就不杀你\NMake me save you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.91,1:25:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\N-Victor. -Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.87,1:25:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白\NElizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.50,1:26:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor! Victor!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.70,1:26:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.33,1:26:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.45,1:27:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但故事并未结束\NBut that was not the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.79,1:27:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着创造生命 结果造就了死亡\NIn seeking life, I created death.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.33,1:27:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看来又要和他们聊聊了\NIt would seem I need to address my men again.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.29,1:27:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.00,1:27:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会听我的话的\NThey'll listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.20,1:28:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！别伤害他！我在这里\NNo, no, stop! Do not harm him! I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.95,1:28:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,带走我吧\NTake me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.87,1:28:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 野兽\NGo on, beast.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.12,1:28:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把我俩都杀了 证明造你的人说的都是真的\NKill us both. Confirm your maker's tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.50,1:28:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,造我的人 说了他的故事\NMy maker… told his tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.87,1:28:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也来说说我的\NThen I will tell you mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.15,1:28:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（第二部分 那头怪物的故事）
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.79,1:28:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多！\NVictor!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.50,1:28:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我反复呼唤你的名字 终于发现这里只有我\NI called your name and understood I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.87,1:32:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是什么？ -开枪！\N-What is that? -Shoot at it!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.29,1:32:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,开枪！\NShoot it!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.95,1:33:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,打到了吗？\NDid you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.62,1:33:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪了？\NWhere is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.08,1:33:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,身上的伤口愈合了\NMy wounds had healed.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.91,1:33:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得寒冷刺骨\NBut I felt cold, so cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.58,1:35:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-能把火生起来吗？ -好\N-Can you start the fire? -All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.62,1:35:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽快把畜栏修好\NAnd I'll repair the corral as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.41,1:35:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 打到了吗？\NYou all right, then? Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.04,1:35:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我们到处看了 就是找不到\NNah, we looked everywhere. Couldn't find that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.45,1:35:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我们朝它开了两枪\NThough we shot at it two times.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.16,1:35:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,血迹在离这里一公里多的地方消失了\NBlood trail died about a mile from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.41,1:35:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好 进来吧\NAll right. Come in. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.83,1:35:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们跟了它一段时间 接着它就消失了\NWe followed it for a while and then it disappeared. Gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.12,1:35:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么东西？熊吗？\NWhat was it? Was it a bear?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.20,1:35:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是熊 也不是人类 我从没见过那样的东西\NThat was no bear or human. I've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.58,1:35:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那么是幽灵吗？\NWas it a ghost, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.04,1:35:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 它流血了 说明它有血肉 有骨头\NIt was no ghost. We drew blood. It was flesh and bone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.37,1:35:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边\NCome, come. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.70,1:35:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你还看到了什么\NTell me more about what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.20,1:35:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,安娜玛丽亚 带祖父去壁炉边\NAnna-Maria, take your grandfather over by the fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.20,1:35:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让他暖一暖\NMake sure he's comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.79,1:35:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来 祖父\NOver here, Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.37,1:35:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们钻到了森林深处 还是没找到它\NWe went deep into the forest. Couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.62,1:36:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,会抓到它的\NWe will get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.08,1:36:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-就是要花些时间 -好\N-It'll take time. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.62,1:36:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,安娜玛丽亚 过来\NAnna-Maria, come.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.91,1:36:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 来带我出去\NCome, love. Help me outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.37,1:36:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那位老人触动了我\NThe old man moved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.75,1:36:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他失明的双目充满智慧\NAnd his unseeing eyes were full of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.54,1:36:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人会发出一种声音\NThese people possessed a sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.08,1:36:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,用来和彼此\NUsed it to tell each other
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.00,1:36:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,交流感受和想法\Nabout feelings and ideas.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.16,1:36:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把这种声音叫言语\NThey called them words.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.70,1:37:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,注意看\NPay attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.66,1:37:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.16,1:37:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一个男孩\NA boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.41,1:37:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-再说一遍 -一个男孩\N-And again. -A boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.20,1:37:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 孩子\NVery good, my child.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.91,1:37:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个呢？\NAnd this?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.95,1:37:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一只…一只眼睛\NAn… An eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.79,1:37:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-再说一遍 -一只眼睛\N-And again. -An eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.70,1:37:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 乖孩子\NYeah. Well done. Well done, my girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.79,1:37:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-眼睛 -这个呢？\N-Eye. -And this one?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.87,1:37:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,手\NThe hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.91,1:37:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-很好 -手\N-Very good. -Hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.79,1:37:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,来搭把手\NGive us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.79,1:37:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,用绳子把最大的捆住带回去\NTie a rope around the biggest one back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.25,1:37:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我渴望加入这个家庭\NI longed to be part of this family.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.33,1:37:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天之前要再多储备一些柴火\NWe'll need more kindling before the winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.45,1:37:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得跑几趟\NWe'll take a few trips.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.62,1:37:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,渴望帮他们的忙\NTo be their benefactor.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.12,1:37:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,需要大一点的树干来搭这个\NWe'll need larger trunks for the structure.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.91,1:37:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.83,1:37:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我能为他们做点什么呢？\NWhat could I possibly do for them?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.29,1:37:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,安娜玛丽亚！父亲！\NAnna-Maria! Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.33,1:37:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快来看啊！\NCome! Come and see!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.50,1:38:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊 安娜玛丽亚！\NLook, Anna-Maria!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.16,1:38:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看 还有呢！快看！\NLook, there's more! Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.08,1:38:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这会是谁送来的？\NWho could have done this?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.87,1:38:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是森林精灵\NThe Spirit of the Forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.29,1:38:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得谢谢他\NWe should thank him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.29,1:38:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.41,1:38:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,说“谢谢你 森林精灵”\NSay, "Thank you, Spirit of the Forest."
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.20,1:38:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 森林精灵\NThank you. Thank you, Spirit of the Forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.33,1:38:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.37,1:38:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 看这里\NCome. Look over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.50,1:38:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.62,1:38:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,从此以后 我就成了 他们看不见的守护者\NFrom then on, I became their invisible guardian.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.16,1:38:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,森林精灵\NThe Spirit of the Forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.04,1:38:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也不时对我释放小小的善意\NAnd on occasion, they too extended a small kindness towards me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.33,1:38:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,送上衣服、面包\NClothes, bread.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.75,1:38:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在那段时光\NAnd for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.37,1:39:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,极为短暂的时光\Na brief, brief moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.20,1:39:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我和这个世界相安无事\Nthe world and I were at peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.70,1:39:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上\NCome along. Come along.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.37,1:39:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,进去吧 对\NIn you go. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.33,1:39:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,记得关门\NMake sure you close that gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.79,1:39:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁做的呢？\NWho could have done this?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.66,1:39:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,森林精灵吧\NThe Spirit of the Forest, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.91,1:39:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\NI got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.08,1:39:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,“最终 这个骄傲的年轻男子\N"And in the end, the proud young man
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.87,1:39:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再也找不到他丢失的那只手了\Ncould never find his missing hand."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.16,1:39:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,它变成了石头 他的财富消失了\N"It turned to stone, his fortune gone,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.41,1:39:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他的骄傲 他的土地 都失去了”\Nand he lost his pride and lost his land."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.08,1:39:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好 宝贝\NVery good, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.29,1:39:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,读得真棒 再读下这个吧\NBeautifully read. Now try this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.25,1:40:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,狼来了\NWolves.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.70,1:40:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,某个想法\NAn idea,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.83,1:40:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,某种感觉 在我心中愈发清晰\Na feeling became clear to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.91,1:40:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人并不憎恨狼\NThe hunter did not hate the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.33,1:41:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,狼并不憎恨羊\NThe wolf did not hate the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.41,1:41:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但相互之间的暴力冲突无可避免\NBut violence felt inevitable between them.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.33,1:41:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 也许这正是世界的法则\NPerhaps, I thought, this was the way of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.66,1:41:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你成为猎物 被杀\NIt would hunt you and kill you
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.12,1:41:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因为你的身份\Njust for being who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.08,1:41:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 我月末就会把羊卖掉\NThe sheep will be sold by the end of the month, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.25,1:41:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后带着你 阿尔玛和安娜玛丽亚去镇上住\NThen I'll take you, Alma and Anna-Maria into town.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.70,1:41:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要上山\NWe'll go into the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.95,1:41:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去猎几头狼 冬末回来\Nhunt the wolves and be back at the end of winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.08,1:41:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我每年冬天都在这里祈祷 今年也一样\NI pray here alone every winter and this year will be no different.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.12,1:41:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 求你了 听劝吧\NPlease, Father, listen to reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.83,1:41:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们该怎么做就怎么做 我也一样\NYou do what you must and so will I.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.16,1:41:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老顽固\NYou stubborn old goat.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.25,1:41:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只有你和我了 森林精灵\NIt's just you and I now, Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.50,1:42:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就你和我了\NJust you and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.58,1:42:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经构想了无数种方式\NAnd I had formed in my imagination many ways
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.29,1:42:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在这个老头面前现身\NI would present myself to the old man.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.62,1:42:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他会怕我？\NWould he fear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.41,1:42:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎我？\NWelcome me?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.04,1:42:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还是会赶我走呢？\NTurn me away?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.75,1:42:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在那里？\NWho goes there?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.91,1:42:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,上前一步 我进入了完全不同的世界\NWith a single step, I entered a different world.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.37,1:42:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经我只能远远观望的世界\NOne I had only seen from afar.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.20,1:42:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是谁？\NPlease, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.54,1:42:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,出个声吧\NAnswer me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.91,1:42:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\NTell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.41,1:42:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你来干什么的？\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.33,1:42:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,路过\NTravel.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.79,1:42:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的过客 欢迎你\NWelcome, dear traveler.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.62,1:43:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请你自己找把椅子 不要觉得我怠慢了你\NDo not think me ungrateful for the company if I ask you to procure a chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.50,1:43:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法周到待客\NI… I find it difficult being a good host.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.33,1:43:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.25,1:43:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛看不见\NMy… My sight has failed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.66,1:43:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,桌上有面包和白兰地\NBut there is bread and brandy on the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.75,1:43:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,请自行享用\NPray help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.08,1:43:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,白兰地？\NBran… dy?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.87,1:43:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听你说话\NYour language.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.00,1:43:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好像不大流利\NYou have a hard time speaking it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.91,1:43:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是从别的地方来的？\NAre you not from these parts?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.79,1:43:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕吗？\NAre you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.62,1:43:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不用怕\NNo need to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.87,1:43:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在怕什么？\NWhat are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.25,1:43:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都怕\N-Everything. 
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.37,1:43:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的…\N-Your…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.79,1:43:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手好冷\NYour hands are frozen
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.79,1:43:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还受伤了\Nand you've been hurt, have you not?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.54,1:43:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤？\NHurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.50,1:44:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 你的手上和脸上都有伤疤\NYes. Your hands and face have scars
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.33,1:44:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你还穿着制服\Nand you are wearing uniform.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.04,1:44:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是在战斗中受的伤吗？\NWere you injured in battle?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.12,1:44:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直\NYou were hiding
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.08,1:44:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在磨坊齿轮里面 对吧？\Nin the mill gears, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.08,1:44:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对 你就是森林精灵\NYeah. Yeah. The Spirit of the Forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.33,1:44:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.04,1:44:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不到你的面容\NI cannot judge of your countenance,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.33,1:44:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但听你的嗓音\Nbut there is something in your voice
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.75,1:44:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定很善良\Nwhich persuades me of your goodwill and kindness.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.12,1:44:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,善良？\N-Kindness? -Mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.62,1:44:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,留下来吧\NStay with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.04,1:44:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以吃我的东西 烤我的火\NShare my food and fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.12,1:44:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我有的不多 但能跟你分享 我会很高兴的\NI would be delighted to share what little I have with you
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.08,1:44:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有你陪着我 对我也大有好处\Nand would be greatly helped by your companionship.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.33,1:44:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以读书给我听\NAnd you… you could read to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.95,1:44:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,读书？\N-Read? -Mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.12,1:45:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把这里当成自己家 把我当成朋友\NMake this your home and I your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.50,1:45:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友\NFriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.75,1:45:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友\NFriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.33,1:45:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友\NFriends.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.58,1:45:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在那时 我读到了我生命中第一个故事\NAnd it was then that I read my first story,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.62,1:45:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也是《圣经》中的第一个故事\Nand it was the first story.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.37,1:45:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,故事的主人公是一个名叫亚当的男子 和名叫夏娃的女子\NI read about a man named Adam and a woman named Eve,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.20,1:45:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们住在人类的第一个乐园里\Nabout their time in the first garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.45,1:45:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我读到了两座城市崛起 相互竞争\NI read about the rise of rival cities
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.16,1:45:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一座高塔倒塌\Nand the collapse of a tower
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.41,1:45:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝震怒毁城\Nand the wrath of a God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.33,1:45:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我读到人类斗巨龙\NAnd I read about men that fought dragons
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.83,1:46:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,最终失去一切\Nand men who lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.37,1:46:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,时光流逝\NAnd time passed
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.62,1:46:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如秋叶飘落\Nand fell away with the leaves of autumn.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.54,1:46:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的朋友 你见过下雪吗？\NHave you never seen the snow, my dear friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.33,1:46:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大雪荡涤一切 让世界焕然一新\NIt makes the world clean… and new.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.00,1:46:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“吾乃奥兹曼迪亚斯 万王之王\N"My name is Ozymandias, King of Kings."
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.33,1:46:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,盖世功业 敢叫天公折服\N"Look on my works, ye Mighty, and despair."
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.95,1:46:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,此外无一物\N"No thing beside remains."
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.75,1:46:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但见废墟周围 寂寞平沙空莽莽\N"Round the decay of that colossal wreck, boundless and bare."
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.16,1:46:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,伸向荒凉的四方\N"The lone and level sands stretch far away."
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.50,1:46:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,吾乃奥兹曼迪亚斯”\N"My name is Ozymandias…"
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.20,1:47:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,世上哪里的书比这里还多？\NAre there more books than this in the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.75,1:47:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定还有一些地方\NA few more, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.37,1:47:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这里\NNot here.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.83,1:47:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,左边最后 就拿那本\NLast book on the left. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.33,1:47:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那本还没读过\NWe haven't got to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.45,1:47:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,弥尔顿的《失乐园》\NParadise Lost, Milton.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.29,1:47:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人类对上帝有疑问\NMan has questions for God.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.95,1:47:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就连上帝自己也有疑问\NEven God has questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.04,1:47:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得上帝也想得到答案 所以才会派来自己的儿子\NI think he wanted answers and that is why he sent us his son.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.33,1:47:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他很想了解死亡\NDeath probably intrigued him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.41,1:47:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,了解受苦受难\NSuffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.45,1:47:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道我是谁\NI want to know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.16,1:47:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我从哪里来？\NWhere do I come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.45,1:47:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝拿走了你的记忆 而我多么希望我的记忆也被带走\NGod took your memory just as I wish he would take mine away.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.20,1:47:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,多年前 我拿走了某个人的生命\NMany years ago, I took a man's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.16,1:47:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个好人\NA good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.62,1:48:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,自那时起 我一直在赎罪\NAnd I have been atoning for it since.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.33,1:48:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,试着原谅\NForgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.12,1:48:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,试着忘记\NForget.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.66,1:48:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,智慧真正的试金石\NThe true measure of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.79,1:48:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是知道自己受了伤害\NTo know you have been harmed,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.00,1:48:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,知道被谁伤害\Nby whom you have been harmed,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.25,1:48:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后选择让一切烟消云散\Nand choose to let it all fade.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.20,1:48:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但记不起来的东西 要怎么忘记\NBut I cannot forget what I cannot remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.25,1:48:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都记不起来吗？\NDo you recall nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.12,1:48:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在睡梦中\NIn my dreams…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.62,1:48:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我…能窥见记忆\N…I… see memories.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.20,1:48:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,各种各样的人\NDifferent men.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.20,1:48:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,都是…一些片断\NAll… pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.00,1:48:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\NI…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.33,1:49:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得有火 有水\NI remember f… fire and water.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.25,1:49:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,脚下有沙子\NAnd sand under my feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.33,1:49:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个词\NAnd a word.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.25,1:49:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就一个词\NA single word.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.20,1:49:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么词？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.29,1:49:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.58,1:49:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,去找到它\NGo to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.79,1:49:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NThe word.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.75,1:50:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我终于体会到了\NAnd then I learned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.70,1:50:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真相的可怖\NThe horror of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.70,1:50:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了 自己一无是处\NI understood that I was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.16,1:50:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是个可怜虫\NA wretch.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.08,1:50:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是块不起眼的污渍\NA blot.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.91,1:50:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至算不上是人类\NNot even of the same nature as man.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.25,1:50:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这种痛苦缠绕着我\NThis hurt clung to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.75,1:50:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,永不消散\NIt never let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.87,1:51:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我看见了\NThen I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.08,1:51:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字\NYour name.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.20,1:51:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,“维克多·弗兰肯斯坦”\N"Victor Frankenstein."
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.79,1:51:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了到哪里能找到你\NAnd where to find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.00,1:51:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.50,1:52:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.29,1:53:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了\NYou came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.79,1:53:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我是谁了\NI found what I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.29,1:53:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我是什么造就的了\NWhat I am made from.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.41,1:53:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我是尸骨堆里造出来的\NI am… the child of a charnel house.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.33,1:53:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是残骸\NA wreckage.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.91,1:53:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是用垃圾和被丢弃的尸体拼凑出来的\NAssembled from refuse and the discarded dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.91,1:53:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是怪物\NA monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.70,1:53:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是谁\NI know what you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.20,1:53:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人\NA good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.20,1:53:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我的朋友\NAnd… you are my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.45,1:54:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友？\NFriend?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.58,1:54:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友\NFriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.83,1:54:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\NWhat is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.79,1:54:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是森林里的那东西吗？\NThe-- The thing from the woods?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.91,1:54:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他怎么了？\NWhat have you done to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.33,1:54:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\NDon't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.58,1:54:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快！上膛！杀了它！\NQuick! Reload! Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.00,1:55:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一切重回寂静\NThere was silence again,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.33,1:56:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而冷酷无情的生活还将继续\Nand then… merciless life.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.87,1:56:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我死了多久？\NHow long did I die for?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.37,1:56:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\NI do not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.37,1:56:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但我看到身上的伤口愈合了\NBut I saw my injuries healed.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.75,1:56:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,冬日的寒风直灌入肺\NThe cold winter air stung in my lungs.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.50,1:56:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,孤独感更甚以往 且前所未有\NI felt lonelier than ever,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.62,1:56:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为对世人而言 治愈一切痛苦的良药\Nbecause for every man there was but one remedy to all pain:
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.54,1:56:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有死亡 而这恩赐你也狠心剥夺\NDeath, a gift you too had denied me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.04,1:56:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的内心涌起羡慕之情\NEnvy rose within me
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.08,1:56:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,遂决意向你索求一份恩典\Nand decided to demand a single grace from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.33,1:57:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的缔造者\NMy creator.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.37,1:57:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要…一个同伴\NI would demand… a companion.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.54,1:57:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,起来吧\NI need you to get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.29,1:57:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NYes, of course. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.91,1:57:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,婚礼马上要开始了 你得陪在我身边\NThe wedding will start soon and I want you by my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.41,1:57:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是你天性善良\NIt's hard to believe,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.75,1:57:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不敢相信这话是你说的\Nif not for your kind nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.83,1:58:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟几位宾客说了调查的事\NI've spoken to a few guests about the inquest.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.12,1:58:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,关于那场爆炸的调查\NAbout the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.00,1:58:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们中的大多数都接受了官方的说法\NThe majority accept it for what it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.45,1:58:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,官方怎么说 威廉？\NAnd what was it, William?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.87,1:58:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都过去了 维克多\NThe past, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.62,1:58:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是场可怕的意外\NA terrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.29,1:58:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想卖了那座庄园\NI intend to sell the estate.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.50,1:58:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只有彼此了\NAll we have is each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.25,1:58:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,往四面八方撒\NI want you to throw the petals everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.25,1:58:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都撒一点\NThrow them everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.20,1:58:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,到楼上去 再多撒点\NGo upstairs and do some more of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.37,1:59:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 婚礼前见新娘会带来厄运\NI know it is bad luck to see the bride before the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.45,1:59:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只对新郎起效\NOnly for the groom.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.41,1:59:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 对我没用\NYes, that's right. Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.16,1:59:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊 伊丽莎白\NHello, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.29,1:59:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我从未感受过懊悔 而现在懊悔充斥了我的内心\NI've rarely felt remorse before and now I feel little else. I…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.50,1:59:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心被一种冲动占据已久 但这种感觉已经消散\NA fever gripped me for so long, but it has passed,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.75,1:59:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以正常地面对你了\Nand I see you now as I should.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.45,1:59:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 我衷心祝愿\NFor whatever it's worth, I… I wish you and my little brother,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.70,1:59:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我挚爱的弟弟幸福\Nwho I love more than life, the very best.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.16,1:59:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你大可以自欺欺人\NYou may like to believe you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.16,1:59:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而我都害怕听见\NAnd I dread to even hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.20,1:59:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是我的大喜之日 我就求你一件事\NOn my wedding day, I ask you but for a single grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.16,2:00:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别撒谎了\NNo more lies.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.79,2:00:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-我想告诉你… -给我出去\N-I-- I want to tell you-- -Leave my chambers now.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.08,2:00:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-伊丽莎白 -出去！\N-Elizabeth. -Leave!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.08,2:01:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 别躲在暗处\NCome out of the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.16,2:01:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在这里\Nif you are here.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.91,2:01:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你是来感谢我的吗？\NAre you here to thank me?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.75,2:01:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你活下来了 还变得足够聪明 都找到我了\NYou survived and are intelligent enough to have found me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.29,2:01:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是我造得好\NI made you well.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.79,2:01:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你给我造一个同伴\NI need you to make a companion for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.16,2:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这样的\NOne like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.29,2:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴？\NA com… A companion?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.04,2:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.33,2:01:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,再来个怪物\NAnother monster.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.33,2:01:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.20,2:01:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们两个怪物作伴\NWe can be monsters together.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.58,2:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我付出巨大代价 才找回了理智\NI have found sanity at such a cost,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.12,2:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你却想让我再回疯狂\Nand you here… are madness calling me back.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.58,2:02:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我死不了\NI cannot die.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.25,2:02:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我自己\NAnd I cannot live…
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.91,2:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我也活不好\Nalone.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.16,2:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我造出了非常恐怖的东西\NIn you I have created something truly horrible.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.08,2:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是东西\NNot something.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.91,2:02:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是人\NSomeone.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.66,2:02:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你造出了人\NYou made someone.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.62,2:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.45,2:02:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我多么让人费解 但我会思考\NWhatever puzzle I am, creator, I think.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.16,2:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有感受\NI feel.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.87,2:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有这一个请求\NI have this sole petition…
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.45,2:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再造一个像我一样的\NMake one like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:54.29,2:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢？\NAnd then what?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.50,2:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,生育\NProcreation.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.00,2:03:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,繁殖\NReproduction.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.45,2:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,建立家庭？\NA home?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.54,2:03:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,建造坟墓？\NA grave?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.54,2:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡与破坏不断上演\NDeath begetting death begetting death.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.33,2:03:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,恶魔的种族在地球上蔓延\NA race of devils propagated upon the earth.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.66,2:03:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,肮脏永不断绝\NObscenity perpetuating itself.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.41,2:03:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在你看来我很肮脏 在我看来我只是我\NI am obscene to you, but to myself I simply am.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.00,2:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开！\NBegone!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.62,2:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会再造一个 像你这么邪恶丑陋的东西\NNever again will I make something like you, wicked and deformed.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.29,2:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切还不都是 源自你的执念 维克多\NThen it is still all about your will, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.08,2:03:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,凭恐怖的执念造就我 如今又固执地谴责我\NThat horrible, horrible will that birthed me condemns me now?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.70,2:03:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我开口说话算不上奇迹 你愿意倾听才算！\NThe miracle is not that I should speak, but that you would ever listen!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.08,2:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你不愿赐我伴侣 我将倾泻怒火\NIf you are not to award me love, then I will indulge in rage.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.41,2:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,无穷无尽的怒火\NAnd mine is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.20,2:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,请让一让\NStep aside.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.58,2:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.87,2:04:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.66,2:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你\NYou…
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.62,2:04:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你\NYou…
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.66,2:04:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\NIt's you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.87,2:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白 离它远一点！\NElizabeth, move away from it!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.70,2:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.66,2:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西袭击了她！\NIt attacked her! It attacked her!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:32.95,2:05:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,带我走吧\NTake me with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.83,2:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.20,2:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别动 让我来…我能救你\NNo, let me… I can save you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.58,2:06:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会救活你\NI can save you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:20.33,2:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,救我？\NFrom what?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.41,2:06:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是害我吧\NFrom you?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.33,2:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕你 维克多\NI fear you, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.79,2:06:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo, no…
Dialogue: 0,2:06:28.00,2:06:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一直怕你\NI always have.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.95,2:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你的每一次疯狂和破坏\NEvery ounce of madness and destruction.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.58,2:06:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如同大火 足以吞噬一切\NThe very conflagration that devoured everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.08,2:06:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是你造成的\NIt all came from you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.45,2:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是怪物\NYou are the monster.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:21.04,2:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我和这个世界格格不入\NMy place was never in this world.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.12,2:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直渴望并追寻着 一种说不清道不明的东西\NI sought and longed for something I could not quite name.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.58,2:07:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可在你身上 我找到了这种东西\NBut in you, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.75,2:07:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,丢失并被寻回\NTo be lost and to be found,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.20,2:07:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是爱的宿命\Nthat is the lifespan of love.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.20,2:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,其短暂\NAnd in its brevity,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.87,2:07:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,其悲剧性\Nits tragedy…
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.20,2:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,造就永恒\Nthis has been made eternal.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.83,2:08:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我在你的注视之中\NBetter this way… to fade…
Dialogue: 0,2:08:03.29,2:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,死去吧\Nwith your eyes gazing upon me.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.20,2:08:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她走了 我也想随她而去\NShe is gone and I long to follow.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:56.12,2:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你给了我备受唾弃的生命\NYou gave me life unwanted.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.58,2:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就还给你\NI give that back to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.20,2:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你当我是怪物\NYou thought me a monster.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:04.95,2:09:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我这个怪物来回敬你\NNow I return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.37,2:09:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我 现在就杀了我\NKill me! Kill me now, do it!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.41,2:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让你流血\NI will make you bleed.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.00,2:09:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让你卑微求饶\NI will make you humble.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.87,2:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是造了我\NYou may be my creator,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.12,2:09:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但从今天起 你要听我的话\Nbut from this day forward, I will be your master.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.04,2:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了猎杀我\NYou hunted me past the forests,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.95,2:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,翻山越岭\Npast the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.54,2:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,横跨冰川\Npast frozen horizons,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.08,2:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,直到天地间\Nuntil there was nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.58,2:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩你我\NJust you… and me.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.12,2:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,给我来点子弹\NI need ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.29,2:10:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这个磨快一点\NSharpen this.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.79,2:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来三罐炼乳 一点木柴\NThree cans of condensed milk, some firewood.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.04,2:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还有六筒炸药\NAnd six sticks of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.58,2:10:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,六筒？\NSix?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.37,2:11:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你要打什么？\NWhat are you hunting?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.25,2:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大的\NBig game.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.50,2:12:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.33,2:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.12,2:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只有被我伤到 你才会听我说话\NYou only listen when I hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:41.33,2:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 你相信这东西\NThis. You put your faith in this.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.95,2:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,能够摧毁我\NYou think this will unmake me.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.70,2:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,点着吧 希望如你所愿 但如果失败了\NLight it then and hope it does, but if it does not,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.08,2:12:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再来找你\NI will come for you again.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:57.79,2:12:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,点起来！\NLight it!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:06.70,2:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑吧\NNow… run.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.12,2:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 如今你残破不堪\NSo, there you were, broken and discarded.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:53.75,2:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而我\NAnd I,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.45,2:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,又活过来了\Nalive again.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:03.04,2:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我能感到 被灼伤的血肉在重新生长\NI could feel my singed flesh regrowing.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:08.79,2:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,断裂的骨头重回原位\NThe crackling of my bones resetting.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:13.91,2:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,永不停息的心脏泵出汩汩的血流\NThe murmur of my blood pumping through my incessant heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.37,2:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再次发现无人怜悯\NAnd once more finding no mercy,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.83,2:14:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我只剩一条路可走\NI had but one path.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.45,2:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们终究走到了这一步\NAnd here we are.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.62,2:14:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,精疲力尽 一无所有\NSpent and done.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.33,2:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,再没有什么可以付出或索取了\NNo more in us to give or take.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:53.20,2:14:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,帐篷外的血迹\NThe blood outside the tent…
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.12,2:14:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的\NIt is mine.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:57.33,2:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的\NAll mine.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.00,2:15:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我将流血\NI will bleed.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.83,2:15:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,疼痛\NAche.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.87,2:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,受苦\NSuffer.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.12,2:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,永无尽头\NYou see, it will never end.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:31.91,2:15:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.95,2:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的内心充满懊悔\NRegret consumes me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:44.12,2:15:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如今我终于能正视我的生命了\NAnd I now regard my life for what it was.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:49.16,2:15:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,缔造者 你要走了\NYou will go now, creator.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:54.41,2:15:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要消失了\NFade away.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.70,2:16:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都只是短暂的一瞬\NIt will all be but a brief moment.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.04,2:16:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的诞生 我的悲伤\NMy birth. My grief.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:06.91,2:16:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的损失\NYour loss.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.95,2:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会受惩罚\NI will not be punished.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:14.66,2:16:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,也无法摆脱罪责\NNor absolved.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:20.83,2:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的希望\NWhat hope I had,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:23.20,2:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我的怒火\Nwhat rage…
Dialogue: 0,2:16:26.54,2:16:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,都毫无意义\NIt is all nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:31.20,2:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那股造就我的浪潮 如今要带你走了\NThe tide that brought me here now comes to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.16,2:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,留下搁浅的我\NLeaving me stranded.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:47.79,2:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我吧\NForgive me.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:51.25,2:16:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,吾儿\NMy son.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:00.75,2:17:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如你有意 也请宽恕自己的存在\NAnd if you have it in your heart, forgive yourself into existence.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:06.04,2:17:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,吾儿 如果无法死去 还请细思此事\NIf death is not to be, then consider this, my son.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:11.08,2:17:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,既然活着\NWhile you are alive,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:13.66,2:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,除了活下去 还有别的选择吗？\Nwhat recourse do you have but to live?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.87,2:17:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,活着\NLive.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:26.62,2:17:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说出我的名字吧\NSay my name.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.70,2:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是父亲起的\NMy father gave me that name,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:33.12,2:17:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实并无意义\Nand it meant nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:36.95,2:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我请求你把这个名字还给我\NNow I ask you to give it back to me…
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.75,2:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次了\None last time.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:44.95,2:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就像最开始 你把这个名字\NThe way you said it at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:48.29,2:17:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当成全世界时那样呼唤我\NWhen it meant the world to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:56.29,2:17:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\NVictor.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:00.50,2:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我宽恕你\NI forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:25.08,2:18:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,安息吧 父亲\NRest now, Father.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:32.16,2:18:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,或许现在\NPerhaps now,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:35.45,2:18:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都能算作是人了\Nwe can both be human.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:47.37,2:18:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放下武器\NWeapons down.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.00,2:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-放下武器 -我要为我的人负责\N-Put the weapons down! -I am responsible for my men.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.45,2:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让他走\NHe can leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.58,2:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,船能动了！\NWe are free!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:29.75,2:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们自由了！\NWe are free!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.50,2:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,船长\NCaptain…
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.79,2:20:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,您的指令是？\NWhat are your orders?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:36.25,2:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,扬帆起航\NMan the sails.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.83,2:20:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,掉头\NTurn around.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:38.79,2:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,您要亲自宣布吗？\NDo you want to tell the men?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.70,2:20:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大家听好！\NMen!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:42.95,2:20:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开船回家\NWe're sailing home!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.83,2:20:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回家了\NWe're sailing home!
